Ranchos Penitas West first appeared as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2000 U.S. census]].<ref name=2000CensusTX/> Prior to the [[2010 U.S. census]], the [[Los Minerales, Texas|Los Minerales CDP]] was carved out from its territory.<ref name=2010CensusTX/>

